e Enterprises, Inc.]]|location=[[Napa, California]]|url=http://napavalleyregister.com/news/article_8bd57af0-e670-569c-bc48-9a507d636de6.html|date=July 2, 2015|accessdate=October 18, 2015}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"CIAbuys\">{{cite news|last=Huffman|first=Jennifer|title=CIA buys long-vacant Copia for food offerings|newspaper=Napa Valley Register|publisher=Lee Enterprises, Inc.|location=Napa, California|url=http://napavalleyregister.com/news/article_6a0b3a67-903c-5376-9b14-710037dfffaa.html|date=October 30, 2015|accessdate=November 4, 2015}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hosp2\">{{cite web|title=CIA Cooks Up New Bachelor of Science in Hospitality Management|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=https://www.ciachef.edu/cia-hospitality-management-bachelors-degree-release/|date=May 25, 2017|accessdate=May 30, 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Masters\">{{cite web|title=Online Master's Degree Helps Busy Professionals Create Next Big Thing in Food|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=https://www.ciachef.edu/cia-masters-degree-release/|date=July 19, 2018|accessdate=December 5, 2018}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NYTlist\">{{cite news|last=Collins|first=Glenn|title=Culinary School\u2019s Dining Room to Get Fresh Air|newspaper=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/04/dining/culinary-institute-to-renovate-a-teaching-restaurant.html|date=July 2, 2012|accessdate=April 17, 2016}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Restaurants\">{{cite web|title=New York Campus Restaurants|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=http://www.ciachef.edu/cia-restaurants-learning-by-doing/|accessdate=April 2, 2016}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"PostRoad\">{{cite news|last=Sprong|first=Alison|title=Post Road Pop-Up|newspaper=La Papillote|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|date=January 20, 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Athletics\">{{cite web|title=CIA Athletics|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=http://www.ciachef.edu/athletics/|accessdate=April 2, 2016}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"StHelena\">{{cite web|titl