\">{{cite web|title=The CIA Announces The Creation of its Fourth Campus; The Culinary Institute of America, Singapore|publisher=[[Singapore Institute of Technology]]|url=http://www.singaporetech.edu.sg/press-centre/the-cia-announces-the-creation-of-its-fourth-campus-the-culinary-institute-of-america-singapore-2|date=September 7, 2010|accessdate=April 11, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821154804/http://www.singaporetech.edu.sg/press-centre/the-cia-announces-the-creation-of-its-fourth-campus-the-culinary-institute-of-america-singapore-2|archive-date=August 21, 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Nonprofit\">{{cite web|title=A Not-For-Profit Culinary College|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=http://www.ciachef.edu/not-for-profit/|accessdate=October 18, 2015}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"SelfStudy\">{{cite book|title=CIA Self-Study|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|date=April 2001|via=CIA Archives and Special Collections}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Admins\">{{cite web|title=President's Cabinet|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=https://www.ciachef.edu/administration/|accessdate=June 19, 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hosp1\">{{cite web|title=CIA Hospitality Management Bachelor's Degree|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=https://www.ciachef.edu/cia-new-york-hospitality-management-bachelors-degree-program/|accessdate=May 30, 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Programs\">{{cite web|title=Degree and Certificate Programs|publisher=The Culinary Institute of America|url=http://www.ciachef.edu/degree-and-certificate-programs/|accessdate=May 31, 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"MastersWine\">{{cite news|title=New Napa Valley wine program management master's degree from The Culinary Institute of America|newspaper=North Bay Business Journal|location=[[Napa, California]]|url=https://www.northbaybusinessjournal.com/northbay/sonomacounty/9250662-181/cia-napa-wine-business-education|date=February 5, 2019|accessdate=June 17, 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Accreditation